WEBVTT

00:00.692 --> 00:03.860
<i>Nine years ago,</i>
<i>I witnessed my mother's murder.</i>

00:04.324 --> 00:08.242
<i>I would have been killed, too,</i>
<i>if it hadn't been for Vincent.</i>

00:08.244 --> 00:11.412
<i>I was part of an experimental</i>
<i>special forces group.</i>

00:11.414 --> 00:14.432
<i>Their goal was to create</i>
<i>the perfect super soldier.</i>

00:14.434 --> 00:16.834
<i>They made us stronger,</i>
<i>faster, better.</i>

00:16.836 --> 00:18.719
<i>But something went wrong.</i>

00:18.721 --> 00:20.004
You're him.

00:20.006 --> 00:23.707
She makes me feel like
I have a life again.

00:23.709 --> 00:26.377
Vincent, I need you.
Someone took Evan.

00:31.818 --> 00:33.718
I don't know how
we cover this one up.

00:33.720 --> 00:34.902
Evan heard the whole attack.

00:34.904 --> 00:37.121
Be as normal as you
can possibly be.

00:37.123 --> 00:39.507
<i>No one needs to know you have</i>
<i>anything to do with us.</i>

00:39.509 --> 00:41.926
Whatever killed Peter,

00:41.928 --> 00:43.661
it wasn't entirely human.

00:43.663 --> 00:44.829
Vincent, you all right?

00:46.498 --> 00:49.033
<i>He's dangerous, and if he's not</i>
<i>in control of himself,</i>

00:49.035 --> 00:51.085
<i>somebody needs to be.</i>

00:51.087 --> 00:52.303
No, you can't keep him in that.

00:52.305 --> 00:55.456
We are going to figure out
a way to fix this.

00:56.793 --> 01:03.681
♪

